menu "RedMole HTTP Client"

    config REDMOLE_HTTP_POLL_INTERVAL_MS
        int "API poll interval (ms)"
        default 10000
        help
            How often the HTTP client polls the remote API in milliseconds.

    config REDMOLE_HTTP_RESPONSE_BUF_SIZE
        int "Size of response buffer (bytes)"
        default 10240
        help
            How big the buffer used for storing the response.json string should be

endmenu